                            individual arbitration and you waive your rights to a jury trial
                            and/or to participate in a class-action lawsuit or class-wide
                            arbitration, so explained below.
                        </p>

                        <p class="fs-md-18 fs-14 fw-400 mt-20">
                            This agreement is subject to changes as explained below.
                        </p>

                        <p class="fs-md-18 fs-14 fw-400 mt-20">
                            We may change these terms at any time and as required by law. This
                            may include changing, adding, or removing terms. We may do this in
                            response to legal, business, competitive environment or other
