                            and acknowledge that <span >ZEPETIDES Weight Loss Wellness &amp; Recovery,</span> is a
                            third-party beneficiary of the Medical Consent and has the right
                            to enforce it against you.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
                        <h6>Use By Minors</h6>
                        <p class="fs-md-18 fs-14 fw-400 mt-20">
                            The Service is not intended for use by anyone under the age of
                            eighteen (18) and anyone under the age of eighteen (18) is
                            prohibited from using any part of the Service and/or the Platform,
                            except as to read these Terms and Conditions.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
                        <h6>Your Relationship with Us</h6>
                        <p class="fs-md-18 fs-14 fw-400 mt-20">
                            As part of the Service we make available certain products and
                            services sold and/or offered by us and by third-party providers
                            (medical and/or nursing care), pharmacies, diagnostics
                            laboratories, and other vendors via our Service.
                        </p>
                        <p class="fs-md-18 fs-14 fw-400 mt-20">
